#. module: theme_bookstore
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_bookstore.s_text_image
msgid ""
"<br/>\n"
"        Discover all the publications. There is probably your next favorite book amoung them."
msgstr ""
"<br/>\n"
"        Oplev alle udgivelserne. Din næste yndlingsbog er sikkert blandt dem."

#. module: theme_bookstore
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_bookstore.s_image_text
msgid ""
"<br/>\n"
"        Discover the history of Belgium in this well-documented book with many illustrations and testimonials."
msgstr ""
"<br/>\n"
"        Oplev Belgiens historie i denne veldokumenterede bog med mange "
"illustrationer og vidnesbyrd."

#. module: theme_bookstore
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_bookstore.s_three_columns
